data.title: Washington State News Network
data.meta_description: Merrick Parnell is a news reporter at NewsRadio 610 KONA. He is originally from Orcas Island and before moving to the Tri-Cities he lived in Montana. Merrick enjoys sports, movies, reading, history and exploring...
